headline.print_headline: Holden Out 6 to 9 Months After More Knee Surgery
headline.main: Holden Out 6 to 9 Months After More Knee Surgery

lead_paragraph: American midfielder Stuart Holden has undergone another operation to repair ligaments in his right knee and will be sidelined for six to nine months.
